arts.ttl: Messi visits Camp Nou, trains with Argentina, heads to Angola for friendly
arts.sum: Lionel Messi spent this week in Spain, reminiscing about his glory days at FC Barcelona and training with Argentina’s national team, which is scheduled to travel to Angola on Thursday for a Friday friendly match against the Angolan national team. Messi is one of seven Inter Miami players on national team duty during the FIFA break, which falls smack in the middle of the MLS playoffs.
